Question: Do you think it is ok for the government to read your emails for counter-terrorism purposes?
Answer:
i think it is ok to do so as long as it is for the justice purpose. however, such kind of actions must be controled and publiced. people under monitored must be informed. by doing so, we can send signal to terrorism that we are paying attention to this problem and also we make citizens happier to know how we are using their information.